	Exhibit 32.2




	 






	CERTIFICATION PURSUANT TO




	18 U.S.C. SECTION 1350,




	AS ADOPTED PURSUANT TO




	SECTION 906 OF THE SARBANES-OXLEY ACT OF 2002




	 




	In connection with the Quarterly Report of Wayside Technology Group, Inc. (the “Company”) on Form 10-Q for the period ended March 31, 2017 as filed with the Securities and Exchange Commission on the date hereof (the “Report”), I, Kevin  T. Scull, certify, pursuant to 18 U.S.C. §1350, as adopted pursuant to §906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002, that:




	 




	(1)


	The Report fully complies with the requirements of Section 13(a) or 15(d) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934; and




	 




	(2)


	The information contained in the Report fairly presents, in all material respects, the financial condition and results of operations of the Company.




	 








	 






	 








